import { Button, Lable, Col, FormGroup } from 'reactstrap';
import { Formik, Field, Form } from 'formik';

const ContactForm = () => {

    return(
        <Formik
            initialValues={{
                firstName: '',
                lastName: '',
                phoneNum: '',
                email: '', 
                agree: false, 
                contactType: 'By Phone',
                feedback: ''
            }}
        >
        
        <Form>
            <FormGroup row>
                <Lable htmlFor='firstName' md='2'>
                    First Name
                </Lable>
                <Col md='10'>

                </Col>
            </FormGroup>
            <FormGroup row >
                <Lable htmlFor='lastName' md='2'>
                    Last Name
                </Lable>
                <Col md='10'>

                </Col>
            </FormGroup>
            <FormGroup row>
                <Lable htmlFor='phoneNum' md='2'>
                    Phone
                </Lable>
                <Col md='10'>

                </Col>

            </FormGroup>
            <FormGroup row>
                <Lable htmlFor='email' md='2'>
                    Email
                </Lable>
                <Col md='10'>

                </Col>

            </FormGroup>
            <FormGroup row>
                <Lable check md={{ size: 4, offset: 2 }}>

                </Lable>
                <Col md='4'>
                    May I Contact You?
                </Col>

            </FormGroup>
            <FormGroup row>
                <Lable htmlFor='feedback' md='2'>
                    Your Feedback
                </Lable>
                <Col md='10'>

                </Col>

            </FormGroup>
            <FormGroup row>


            </FormGroup>

        </Form>
        </Formik>
    );

};

export default ContactForm;
